    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>天使亦会喋血</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这部融合哥特与文艺复兴盛期风格的动作冒险角色扮演游戏中，夺回陷落的吉尔登纳克城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《血色之月》中，你将化身拿非利人。这是一个暴戾的半人半天使混血种族，为守护人类免遭地狱侵袭而生，身负超凡异能、精通兵刃与近身格斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满野性、可反复挑战的征程中，你将运用血脉贲张的魂系近战格斗，一路斩杀不断进化的恶魔、亡灵、吸血鬼以及地狱秽蔓的可怖造物。最终，你将直面传说中的殒落之神，展开残酷的首领决战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是选择孤身踏上圣战征途，还是与伙伴并肩屠魔，这则预言都将由你来亲手书写。崛起吧，暴虐的战士。血月骑士团在此集结。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/8992c9eac8f0c4a63c170e3c1641fe2a.poster.avif?t=1772054016\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/8992c9eac8f0c4a63c170e3c1641fe2a.webm?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/8992c9eac8f0c4a63c170e3c1641fe2a.mp4?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸式体验暴力美学</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越摄人心魄且愈发险恶的城区与街巷，在征途中夺回吉尔登纳克。这个世界将铭记你的足迹，不断重塑蜕变，亦会疯狂反击，你无需忍受机械重复的折磨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/3ed998d631b7a3cd452b95da571d0a9d.poster.avif?t=1772054016\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/3ed998d631b7a3cd452b95da571d0a9d.webm?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/3ed998d631b7a3cd452b95da571d0a9d.mp4?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>血染征途</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以六翼天使的复仇战技迎战恶魔、亡灵、吸血鬼以及地狱秽蔓的可怖造物，对每类敌人都可施展血脉贲张的专属处决技。这是专为崇尚即兴战斗与华丽杀戮艺术的武者量身打造的修罗场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/146ae61ee675ea9d63871acaa226d340.poster.avif?t=1772054016\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/146ae61ee675ea9d63871acaa226d340.webm?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/146ae61ee675ea9d63871acaa226d340.mp4?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>孤胆远征或并肩屠戮</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的搭档能够提升你的战力。在可选合作模式中共享生命、复活战友、激发协同异能。动态难度调节与敌群配置，让每次任务都如同量身定制的生死试炼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/493e47d17f0d22f793fb2b18172cd8fb.poster.avif?t=1772054016\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/493e47d17f0d22f793fb2b18172cd8fb.webm?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/493e47d17f0d22f793fb2b18172cd8fb.mp4?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>险中求胜</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次征途皆是蜕变与抗争的仪式，每场胜利都将解锁新任务、异变效果与技能成就。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/072cd3c643f1cbdb0c4dea26d1c61952.poster.avif?t=1772054016\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/072cd3c643f1cbdb0c4dea26d1c61952.webm?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/072cd3c643f1cbdb0c4dea26d1c61952.mp4?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>释放天使化身之力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驱动不断进化的拿非利人神力，发动临时异能与天罚级毁灭性打击，在战场掀起神圣风暴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/42fcc5bd8d234b3c9834328309034ee6.poster.avif?t=1772054016\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/42fcc5bd8d234b3c9834328309034ee6.webm?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4317690/extras/42fcc5bd8d234b3c9834328309034ee6.mp4?t=1772054016\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在圣辉庇佑中暂歇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >征伐间隙重返月神教廷总部，这里是获取永久升级、与关键角色交互的基地。整备完毕后，可通过战略沙盘俯瞰全城，谋划下一场圣战。</p>",
